the first comment disposition document contained in <A=20
href=3D"http://www.itscj.ipsj.or.jp/sc34/def/0947.htm">SC 34 N 947</A> =
and the=20
second comment disposition document contained in <A=20
href=3D"http://www.itscj.ipsj.or.jp/sc34/def/1021.htm">SC 34 N 1021.</A> =
The=20
Secretariat is instructed to submit the text to the ITTF for the FDIS =
